descriptionHtml:
This is my Character Kei Valentine, the most beautiful character that i ever made. this is a backup of her CME. I'm planning to reformat my PC, so i made a backup of her face. if somethings go wrong i will go here and download the file.  
[img]http://i.imgur.com/B97QxLy.jpg[/img]

If anyone want to use this CME file just download the mods on credit section. and Copy/paste the CME_save files to Documents > my games > skyrim > CME_saves.

I made this character without ENB. so i'm very proud to it.
